<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">

<head>
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Georgia, serif; /* Change font family to Georgia */
            color: #333; /* Set text color */
            background-color: #cfe4ff; /* Light warm brown background color */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 90%; /* Adjust width to cover majority of the width */
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: ghostwhite; /* Light beige background color */
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .centered-image {
            width: 90%; /* Set image width to 50% of container width */
            max-width: 600px; /* Set maximum width for smaller screens */
            height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
            margin: 0 auto 10px auto; /* Center the image horizontally and reduce space below */
            display: block; /* Ensure the image is treated as a block element */
        }

        h1 {
            color: #CD853F; /* Change font color to match the sub-heading */
            font-size: 36px; /* Increase font size */
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Reduce margin bottom */
            margin-top: 10px; /* Adjusted margin to reduce space at the top */
        }

        .sub-heading {
            color: #CD853F; /* Lighter shade of brown */
            margin-top: 10px; /* Reduce margin top */
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Reduce margin bottom */
        }

        .values {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Reduce margin bottom */
        }

            .values li {
                margin-bottom: 5px; /* Reduce margin bottom */
            }

        .story {
            margin-top: 5px; /* Adjusted margin to reduce space at the top */
            margin-bottom: 5px; /* Reduce margin bottom */
            font-size: 16px; /* Reduce font size further */
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About KhumaloCraft Emporium</h1>

        <!-- Introduction Section -->
        <div class="text-wrap">
            <div class="image-wrap">
                <img src="~/Images/About.jpg" alt="Handcrafted Gifts" class="centered-image">
            </div>
            <p class="description">
                Welcome to KhumaloCraft Emporium, where you can discover a curated collection of handcrafted gifts sourced from artisans across the globe. Our mission is to showcase the artistry and craftsmanship behind each unique item while supporting talented artisans and preserving traditional craft methods.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Our Values Section -->
        <h2 class="sub-heading">Our Values</h2>
        <ul class="values">
            <li><strong>Quality:</strong> We are dedicated to offering top-quality handcrafted products, crafted with meticulous attention to detail.</li>
            <li><strong>Authenticity:</strong> Preserving traditional craft techniques and cultural heritage is at the heart of what we do.</li>
            <li><strong>Fair Trade:</strong> We uphold fair trade principles to ensure that artisans receive fair compensation for their hard work.</li>
            <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> Environmental sustainability is a key focus, and we support eco-friendly practices throughout our supply chain.</li>
            <li><strong>Community:</strong> We foster a sense of community by connecting artisans with customers and promoting cross-cultural exchange.</li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Our Story Section -->
        <h2 class="sub-heading">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="story">
            Established in 2012, KhumaloCraft Emporium started as a passion project to unite artisans and customers on a global scale. From its humble beginnings, it has evolved into a thriving community of artisans, craftsmen, and art enthusiasts driven by a shared passion for creativity and craftsmanship.
        </p>
        <p class="story">
            Today, KhumaloCraft Emporium continues to grow, offering a curated selection of handcrafted products celebrating diverse cultural heritage and artistic traditions worldwide.
        </p>
        <p class="story">
            Today, KhumaloCraft Emporium continues to grow.
        </p>

    </div>
</body>

